    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the keema aloo has had an initial 25 min, remove the dish from the oven and stir through your<strong> blanched peas</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven for a final 5 min or until the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>one pot</strong> <strong>lean beef</strong> <strong>keema aloo matar</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> garlic & coriander naan[s]</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) and put the baking tray[s] in the oven for 3 min or until the bread is warm</p>",
